        <p class="content-sub-heading" style="font-size:25px;">WALKTHROUGH</p>
        <p>1. After successful payment, you will receive a Ticket ID through a mail within 24 hours of payment. <br>2. A QR containing few details will be mailed you in the month of December. Take hard copy of this QR code. <br>3. Entry will be through IIT Bombay main gate only after producing ticket ID, after which you will be given coloured band. <br>4. Report at hospitality desk in Student Activity Center (SAC). <br>5. Produce Your : Ticket ID, QR code hard copy, Gate Pass, Your college ID card & Photocopy of Govt. ID card.<br>6. You will be provided details of allotted room number, hostel number and respective lock passcode.<br>7. Deadline of  checkout is 10:00 am on 1st January. Lock the room before leaving. <br><br> <b> No need to report at Hospitality desk after the check out. You will receive the caution money within 20 working days in your bank account after 1st January. </b><br><br># Caution money will be forfeited for all the residents of the room in following cases:<br>- Any harm done to mattress or hostel property<br>- Missing mattress or door lock<br>- Room left unlocked after checking out<br>- Number Lock passcode changed<br>- Delay in checking out<br>- Kindly visit the hospitality desk, to report some complain.<br></p>
