            <b style='color: #df9111'>Note:</b> The accommodation will be given in groups. The group which is registered below might be given accommodation together and needs to pay the fee together. <br>The accommodation charges do not include food facilities. Guest can purchase their meals from the food court, night cafeteria or private hostel canteens or hostel messes. <br>Boys and girls will be given accommodation in different hostel. <br><br>You will receive a confirmation mail of payment within 24 hours. Mail your teamID, transaction ID, name, amount to <a href="mailto:hospitality@techfest.org">hospitality@techfest.org</a>, if no confirmation mail received.
        </p>
        
